As a user, I want the program to open an interface with the board and all other buttons 

As a user, I want to display a game board, so that I can see the current status of the game

As a user, I want the ability to save my current game, so that I can resume playing later

As a user, I want the ability to load a saved game, so that I can resume what I couldn't finish earlier

As a user, I want the ability to move my pieces by first clicking on such pieces then clicking on a destination for such piece, so that I can visualize how I am interacting with the game

As a user, I want the ability to play with 2 players

As a user, I want the ability to concede defeat at any moment during the game, so that I do not need to finish my game

As a user, I want the ability to see my available moves after clicking on the piece I would like to move, so that I can visualize all of my possible moves

As a new player, I want the ability to pull up instructions on the game, so that I can learn how to play the game
